cat << EOF
The procmail and formail mail processing package can be used to
create mail-servers, mailing lists, sort your incoming mail into
separate folders/files (real convenient when subscribing to one or
more mailing lists or for prioritising your mail), preprocess your
mail, start any programs upon mail arrival (e.g. to generate
different chimes on your workstation for different types of mail) or
selectively forward certain incoming mail automatically to someone.
EOF
